  <div class='container'>
    <div class='terms'>
    <h2>Terms & Conditions</h2>
      <ul>
<li>This program is only applicable to students in the United States.</li>
<li>Open to qualified program participants with a valid college/university ID.</li>
<li>Each Vertagear Student Program discount offer may only be used once and cannot be combined with other programs, promotions, or offers.</li>
<li>Vertagear reserves the right to withdraw, terminate, or amend the terms of sale at any time.</li>
        <li>After verification, you'll receive a <b>one-time discount code</b> to apply during checkout.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

